reviewText: Mostly on Jays birthday party, light demo, really liked the black JJ instructor with his students. other than that  a so-so video

If you are a Wally Jay fan then you will enjoy this over-view of his 90th birthday
celebration. I was hoping to see the same audio visual tribute presentation that was shown
at the birthday dinner but unfortunately that was not included. However, I still enjoyed
the tribute and the demonstrations shown.
